{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Innovations</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ff3d43);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: white;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #ff3d43;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #ff6b6b;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #ff3d43;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff3d43, #e74c3c);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: white;\n            color: #ff3d43;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: white;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">Smart Home Innovations</div>\n        <h1>Your Home, Smarter Than Ever</h1>\n        <p>Experience seamless control, enhanced security, and ultimate convenience with our cutting-edge smart home solutions.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <h2>What We Offer</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Smart Lighting</h3>\n                <p>Control your lights from anywhere. Set schedules, adjust brightness, and create ambiance with a tap.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                <h3>Home Security</h3>\n                <p>Protect your home with smart locks, cameras, and sensors. Receive real-time alerts and monitor your property.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-thermometer-half\"></i>\n                <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                <p>Optimize your home's temperature for comfort and energy savings. Control your thermostat remotely.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-volume-up\"></i>\n                <h3>Entertainment Systems</h3>\n                <p>Integrate your audio and video systems for a unified and immersive entertainment experience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Upgrade Your Living?</h2>\n        <p>Discover the future of home living. Explore our products and see how easy it is to transform your house into a smart home.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Smart Home Innovations. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // JavaScript can be added here for interactive elements if needed\n        // For this example, it's kept minimal to focus on the static design.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}